author: bsunanda
body: Two collections are added - information about L1 trigger information and prerechit collection for HBHE. This changes the o/p from 0.46 MB per stored event to 0.48 MB per event - an increase by 3.8%
title: Run2-alca93 Backport of #20305 change output command for IsoTrack AlCaReco jobs
